~ start
Marcus: Don't get me wrong, I'm not saying you two are incapable of doing anything. He looked like he was at a lot less than peak performance.
Marcus: ...But we all know that I'm the strongest one here by far. Don't worry about coming to help, right now you guys need to rest.
Marcus: Best case scenario, you softening him up will just make this go by faster. In the worst case...I'll make it easier to finish the job.
Marcus: Don't worry about me. He doesn't have a clue what I can do to him.
set TalkScenes.zulie_talk.dialogue_resource = load("res://dialogue/zulie_post_noble_2.dialogue")
do TalkScenes.zulie_talk.start()
=> END